Online Store Name: BookNest
Product/Service Description: An online platform for purchasing books both physical and digital. 
Target Customers: Students, Professionals, Casual Readers, Parents
Key Features:
    • Login & Signup Page (Admin, Staff, Customer)
    • Browse Book Catalog
    • Book categorization
    • Multi-currency support (PHP, USD, etc.)
    • Admin Panel (add, edit or delete books and manage categories)
    • Track Order Status 
    • Featured Books & Staff Picks
    • Staff-Fullfillment Panel (view, process, and mark the status of book orders)

